ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
Traditional financial models rely on static assumptions and manual growth inputs.
This project introduces an automated growth suggestion engine exposed through a FastAPI-based REST API, enabling consistent and data-driven financial forecasting.
The system fetches real financial data using Yahoo Finance (yfinance) and generates suggested growth rates for:
Revenue
EBITDA
Profit After Tax (PAT)

